      <data key="d2">False</data>
      <data key="d3">False</data>
      <data key="d4">0.9</data>
      <data key="d5">[{"quote": "Rowan: I also aligned the modules because Brendan reminded us in the meeting that we had with him that this implementation... if it's going to be used to substantiate his patent application", "ts": 130.0, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Laura: I think probably Brandon will have, some comments around this mainly to make sure, like, remember in the patent it says like, if it's like a natural and legal entity", "ts": 620.0, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "the first case, the 39, 9, 45, which is the case that, Brandon had already looked into.", "ts": 2110.0, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "But we do need Brandon to check that and we need Brandon to check the nice application form.", "ts": 2435.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d6">["chapter:02", "chapter:04", "chapter:11"]</data>
