      <data key="d5">[{"quote": "Deon (chapter 08 summary): Deon reads it as them trying to get the high-level direction right first (Vanessa replied with bullet points).", "ts": 1550.0, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "their latest email, it was just Vanessa replying with like bullet points.", "ts": 1600.0, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "It does match, but I feel that Vanessa is not technical.", "ts": 1900.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
