    <node id="claim:0029">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Starting narrow in one domain is the right way to begin a complex-pipeline POC, despite the overfitting risk</data>
      <data key="d18">False</data>
      <data key="d4">0.9</data>
      <data key="d5">[{"quote": "It is a risk of overfitting, but when, when it's such like a complex pipeline and you're doing a proof of concept, like normally you start in a domain ... because if not, it just gets too broad and it's quite difficult to start.", "ts": 2385.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
